<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    This refers to the killing of Suhasini (Chikkappa's liaison ).Hint is in discussion how Manjunath got rid of his wife and Chikkappa's boast,who he wou<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    This refers to the killing of Suhasini (Chikkappa's liaison ).Hint is in discussion how Manjunath got rid of his wife and Chikkappa's boast,who he would do it.Since narrator did not try to help the women so he feels partner to the crime which is connoted by blood on his hand in end.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
